{"tid":1187001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界只有佢阻止到侵侵","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T10:25:38.000Z","uid":13467,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eda2365e1a30ff48f727147b6a64c8ab1452a6c2","tid":1187001,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=350602&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350602%26refer%3DShare&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=cde30239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350602%26refer%3DShare&h=9f11c310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=350602&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普國事訪問英國是國際新聞焦點，英國一位「官員」更為這則新聞添上趣味。英國內閣辦公廳首席捕鼠大臣，亦即住在首相府的貓咪拉里，不但搶去特朗普風頭，更大膽得妨礙了他行程。<br />\n<br />\n美國《時代》雜誌報道，國事訪問第二日，特朗普與英國首相文翠珊在唐寧街10號舉行雙邊會談。文翠珊在首相府門外迎賓時，拉里一直在窗口「冷眼旁觀」，無意間做了「攝石人」，在英美領導人合照中被攝入鏡。<br />\n<br />\n此舉吸引了傳媒眼球，但拉里似乎食髓知味，會談結束，特朗普準備乘代號「野獸」的專車離開時，拉里再度現身，走到「野獸」車底避雨。<br />\n<br />\n為安全計，「野獸」不敢駛走，特朗普因而在首相府外滯留了一會。有記者打趣說，特朗普行程出現嚴重保安事故。亦有報道說，想不到防彈、防爆、防化武的「野獸」，竟然被一隻貓考起。<br />\n<br />\n拉里則在官方社交賬戶反問，大家忍心要牠在外淋雨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypE77V2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypE77V2.png&h=33f0e785&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c535bb8b51edcc9f78c638cce89a60f294a4c9","tid":1187001,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3ba69007d4d6d41062147be0fecfabe1a8cd35a","tid":1187001,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}